Package uml

This package contains all model classes of the UML representation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UmlAttribute
    Represents an attribute of an UmlClass
    UmlClass
    Represents a class
    UmlElement
    Abstract class extended by UmlClasses, UmlInterfaces and UmlEnumerations
    UmlEnumeration
    Represents an enumeration in a class diagramm
    UmlInterface
    Represents an interface
    UmlLiteral
    Represents a literal of an UmlEnumeration
    UmlModel
    Represents the UML model with its UmlPackages, UmlElements and UmlRelationships
    UmlOperation  
    UmlPackage
    Represents a package in an UmlModel
    UmlParameter
    Represents a parameter of an UmlOperation
    UmlParameterSubstitution
    Represents a parameter substitution of an UmlTemplateBinding
    UmlRelationship
    Represents an relationship with the involved UmlElements, the UmlMultiplicityValues and determined by an UmlRelationshipType
    UmlTemplateBinding
    Represents a template binding of an UmlElement or UmlOperation
    UmlTemplateParameter
    Represents an template parameter of a generic UmlClass or UmlInterface
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    UmlMultiplicityValue
    Defines possible values for multiplicity values in UmlAttributes, UmlRelationships and UmlParameters
    UmlParameterDirection
    Defines possible directions for UmlParameters
    UmlRelationshipType
    Determines the type of an UmlRelationship
    UmlVisibility
    Enumeration to determine the visibility of UmlElements, UmlOperations and UmlAttributes

Package uml Description

This package contains all model classes of the UML representation.
